{
  "number": 90,
  "name": "سُورَةُ البَلَدِ",
  "englishName": "Al-Balad",
  "englishNameTranslation": "The City",
  "revelationType": "Meccan",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 6024,
      "text": "NAY! I call to witness this land –",
      "numberInSurah": 1,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6025,
      "text": "this land in which thou art free to dwell -",
      "numberInSurah": 2,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6026,
      "text": "and [I call to witness] parent and offspring:",
      "numberInSurah": 3,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6027,
      "text": "Verily, We have created man into [a life of] pain, toil and trial.",
      "numberInSurah": 4,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6028,
      "text": "Does he, then, think that no one has power over him?",
      "numberInSurah": 5,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6029,
      "text": "He boasts, \"I have spent wealth abundant!\"",
      "numberInSurah": 6,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6030,
      "text": "Does he, then, think that no one sees him?",
      "numberInSurah": 7,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6031,
      "text": "Have We not given him two eyes,",
      "numberInSurah": 8,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6032,
      "text": "and a tongue, and a pair of lips,",
      "numberInSurah": 9,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6033,
      "text": "and shown him the two highways [of good and evil]?",
      "numberInSurah": 10,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6034,
      "text": "But he would not try to ascend the steep uphill road...",
      "numberInSurah": 11,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6035,
      "text": "And what could make thee conceive what it is, that steep uphill road?",
      "numberInSurah": 12,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6036,
      "text": "[It is] the freeing of one's neck [from the burden of sin],",
      "numberInSurah": 13,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6037,
      "text": "or the feeding, upon a day of [one's own] hunger,",
      "numberInSurah": 14,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6038,
      "text": "of an orphan near of kin,",
      "numberInSurah": 15,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6039,
      "text": "or of a needy [stranger] lying in the dust –",
      "numberInSurah": 16,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6040,
      "text": "and being, withal, of those who have attained to faith, and who enjoin upon one another patience in adversity, and enjoin upon one another compassion.",
      "numberInSurah": 17,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6041,
      "text": "Such are they that have attained to righteousness;",
      "numberInSurah": 18,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6042,
      "text": "whereas those who are bent on denying the truth of Our messages – they are such as have lost themselves in evil,",
      "numberInSurah": 19,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6043,
      "text": "[with] fire closing in upon them.",
      "numberInSurah": 20,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 594,
      "ruku": 532,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ],
